if steamVR can not be launched, please check:

the file openvrpaths.vrpath in the ~/.config/openvr


make the contents of the "config" and "log" as following

{
   "config" : [ "/home/x-arm/.steam/steam/config" ],
   "external_drivers" : null,
   "jsonid" : "vrpathreg",
   "log" : [ "/home/x-arm/.steam/steam/logs" ],
   "runtime" : [ "/home/x-arm/.local/share/Steam/steamapps/common/SteamVR/", "/home/x-arm/.local/share/Steam/steamapps/common/SteamVR" ],
   "version" : 1
}
